WEBVTT

1
00:00:02.766 --> 00:00:03.600
Your Highness.

2
00:00:04.200 --> 00:00:05.866
Let me massage you.

3
00:00:06.400 --> 00:00:07.466
Mm.

4
00:00:10.100 --> 00:00:13.800
Your Highness, the consort has already been sent to the cold palace.

5
00:00:13.800 --> 00:00:16.066
Why are you still sighing?

6
00:00:16.133 --> 00:00:17.033
Dragon Consort.

7
00:00:17.333 --> 00:00:20.666
I used to think she was just a scapegoat.

8
00:00:21.066 --> 00:00:23.200
But the Emperor

9
00:00:23.366 --> 00:00:26.666
is turning the whole palace upside down for her.

10
00:00:26.966 --> 00:00:29.766
Even I am being investigated.

11
00:00:29.766 --> 00:00:33.633
This kind of royal favor was never given to Consort Yan before.

12
00:00:37.000 --> 00:00:37.900
Your Highness.

13
00:00:38.400 --> 00:00:42.300
Are you worried that Consort Rong might become the second Consort Yan?

14
00:00:43.300 --> 00:00:46.600
Then it might be better to send her out of the palace while you still can.

15
00:00:46.600 --> 00:00:48.100
Wouldn’t that be perfect?

16
00:00:48.466 --> 00:00:50.166
I also think so.

17
00:00:51.166 --> 00:00:53.966
But the Emperor has just been betrayed by Consort Yang.

18
00:00:53.966 --> 00:00:55.800
If we lose Consort Rong as well,

19
00:00:56.000 --> 00:00:59.166
I’m worried something might go wrong with the Emperor.

20
00:00:59.166 --> 00:01:01.366
This could lead to turmoil in the court.

21
00:01:05.066 --> 00:01:08.966
You should keep a close watch on Consort Rong and the Emperor’s movements.

22
00:01:09.133 --> 00:01:10.400
For this matter,

23
00:01:10.966 --> 00:01:13.633
I cannot make a hasty decision.

24
00:01:14.166 --> 00:01:16.600
I will arrange it right away.

25
00:01:19.700 --> 00:01:22.366
Your Highness, it’s already past midnight.

26
00:01:22.400 --> 00:01:24.100
It’s still snowing outside.

27
00:01:24.366 --> 00:01:27.600
You should rest early. It’s snowing.

28
00:01:28.966 --> 00:01:31.666
The Emperor said he would come early today.

29
00:01:32.700 --> 00:01:35.266
Never mind, it’s fine if he doesn’t come.

30
00:01:35.666 --> 00:01:37.800
If the Empress Dowager is really willing to let me leave the palace,

31
00:01:38.366 --> 00:01:41.200
I shouldn’t be attached to these romantic feelings anymore.

32
00:01:41.733 --> 00:01:44.666
The Emperor still loves you very much.

33
00:01:45.200 --> 00:01:48.166
Biyuan, help me to bed.

34
00:01:48.166 --> 00:01:51.200
Your Highness, something is wrong!
